<p>When combined with antiemetic drugs and compared to antiemetics alone (9=
 trials, 687 participants, PC6 plus antiemetics reduced vomiting from 33% t=
o 18% (RR 0.56, 95% CI 0.35 =E2=80=93 0.91) and the need for rescue antieme=
tics from 32% to 20% (RR 0.61, 95% CI 0.44 =E2=80=93 0.86) but not nausea (=
48% to 38%, RR 0.79, 95% CI 0.55 =E2=80=93 1.13) but with studies needed to=
 assess this outcome (<span class=3D"tooltipsall classtoolTips16" style=3D"=
